---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p class="long-form">
      The natural path of engagement begins with the individual leader. The CEO gains personal technical capability and structural clarity first, then brings this capacity to the rest of the organization.
    </p>
    <div class="rule"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>For Individuals</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Unlock Session</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>~3hrs</span>
          <span>$1,500</span>
        </div>
        <p>Audit your workflow, set up tools on your devices, and produce immediate payoff. This is the moment a leader crosses from AI-naive to AI-native.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Personal Stack Build</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>2 weeks</span>
          <span>$5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>A sustained engagement to build out your entire personal workflow—tools, integrations, and agent workflows—so you are genuinely AI-native in your daily work.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Sparring Partner</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>Monthly</span>
          <span>$1,500 - $2,500</span>
        </div>
        <p>Ongoing relationship with biweekly sessions and async access. Maintain capability as the frontier moves and receive structural counsel as your situation evolves.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>For Teams</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Discovery</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$3,000 - $5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Survey the current state of the organization's workflows. Map opportunities for AI-native transformation and produce a clear structural picture of where things are and where they should go.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Build</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$8,000 - $15,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Build the actual tools, integrations, and agent workflows that transform how the team operates. We build with the team so they understand what was built.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Train</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$2,500 - $5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Formation programs to make the team AI-native. We ensure the team can operate, maintain, and improve the tools independently, preventing oscillation back to old patterns.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Retainer</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>Monthly</span>
          <span>$2,000 - $4,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Ongoing relationship to keep the team current. Prevent the slide back to AI-naive operations and expand capability as new tools and patterns emerge.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <section class="section">
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <h2>Initiate Contact</h2>
    <p class="long-form">
      Engagement begins with a direct conversation to assess structural fit.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="production-link">Reach out</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
